      "text": "<p>Trebalo bi kreirati novi element tipa <code>button</code> sa tekstom <code>Delete</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "const deleteButton = document.querySelectorAll('button')?.[2]; \r\nassert.match(deleteButton?.textContent ,/delete/gi);"
